Also in the United States, many ESPN commentators call the game Football. So to all those who think the UK is alone in being the only English speaking country that uses Football and not Soccer, think again. Also the former British West Indies countries and English speaking African countries also call Association Football, by the name of Football. [[User:Footballworldworldfootball|Footballworldworldfootball]] ([[User talk:Footballworldworldfootball|talk]]) 03:32, 9 February 2009 (UTC)

